00:35:48.420 --> 00:35:51.980 align:middle line:84%
You take people coming out
of Africa 100,000 years ago,

00:35:51.980 --> 00:35:54.350 align:middle line:84%
you give them a shave,
three piece suit,

00:35:54.350 --> 00:35:56.830 align:middle line:84%
and put them on a
Wall Street, and they

00:35:56.830 --> 00:35:59.840 align:middle line:84%
look like all the other
barbarians on Wall Street.

00:35:59.840 --> 00:36:04.560 align:middle line:84%
Genetically the same, OK,
doing the same kind of antics

00:36:04.560 --> 00:36:06.970 align:middle line:84%
that we see the
people on Wall Street.

00:36:06.970 --> 00:36:08.220 align:middle line:90%
Let's do a science experiment.

00:36:08.220 --> 00:36:10.053 align:middle line:84%
Let's all take a subway
train to Wall Street

00:36:10.053 --> 00:36:13.020 align:middle line:90%
and you'll see what I mean.

00:36:13.020 --> 00:36:15.880 align:middle line:84%
Well, now we have
nuclear weapons.

00:36:15.880 --> 00:36:20.470 align:middle line:84%
But the same primitive
tribal instincts

00:36:20.470 --> 00:36:24.070 align:middle line:84%
that govern us throughout
most of existence,

00:36:24.070 --> 00:36:28.410 align:middle line:84%
99.9% of our human exist--
we lived in small tribes.

00:36:28.410 --> 00:36:31.350 align:middle line:84%
Small tribes of
maybe 100 people,

00:36:31.350 --> 00:36:34.030 align:middle line:90%
led by some charismatic leader.

00:36:34.030 --> 00:36:35.000 align:middle line:90%
100 people.

00:36:35.000 --> 00:36:36.840 align:middle line:90%
That was our universe.

00:36:36.840 --> 00:36:38.620 align:middle line:84%
And what defined us
was the fact that we

00:36:38.620 --> 00:36:42.385 align:middle line:84%
were members of a tribe in
opposition to other tribes.

00:36:42.385 --> 00:36:44.440 align:middle line:90%
Well, that got us into war.

00:36:44.440 --> 00:36:46.760 align:middle line:84%
And that got us into
a lot of mischief.

00:36:46.760 --> 00:36:49.440 align:middle line:90%
Now we have nuclear weapons.

00:36:49.440 --> 00:36:51.670 align:middle line:90%
Now we have global warming.

00:36:51.670 --> 00:36:55.200 align:middle line:84%
And now we're truly, on a
cosmic scale, messing up

00:36:55.200 --> 00:36:56.620 align:middle line:90%
the planet Earth.

00:36:56.620 --> 00:36:58.670 align:middle line:84%
And the question
is, can we extend

00:36:58.670 --> 00:37:03.340 align:middle line:84%
our definition of a tribe
to the entire planet?

00:37:03.340 --> 00:37:05.760 align:middle line:84%
If we make the technical
transition to type one,

00:37:05.760 --> 00:37:09.090 align:middle line:84%
are we going to make a
conscious decision to think,

00:37:09.090 --> 00:37:12.110 align:middle line:84%
as a planetary civilization
with limited resources,

00:37:12.110 --> 00:37:15.180 align:middle line:84%
with finite ability
to pollute the planet,

00:37:15.180 --> 00:37:17.290 align:middle line:90%
it's not clear at all.

00:37:17.290 --> 00:37:18.190 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:37:18.190 --> 00:37:22.430 align:middle line:84%
One day, during the '80s,
Ronald Reagan met Gorbachev.

00:37:22.430 --> 00:37:24.910 align:middle line:84%
And they had a
fascinating discussion.

00:37:24.910 --> 00:37:26.980 align:middle line:84%
One thing you have to
hand it to Ronald Reagan,

00:37:26.980 --> 00:37:31.330 align:middle line:84%
he was able to reduce everything
in terms of Hollywood.

00:37:31.330 --> 00:37:33.300 align:middle line:90%
That was his world view.

00:37:33.300 --> 00:37:34.530 align:middle line:90%
Hollywood.

00:37:34.530 --> 00:37:37.090 align:middle line:84%
And Gorbachev asked
Reagan a question.

00:37:37.090 --> 00:37:41.040 align:middle line:84%
Under what circumstances
can we work together?

00:37:41.040 --> 00:37:42.390 align:middle line:90%
I'm a communist, he said.

00:37:42.390 --> 00:37:43.770 align:middle line:90%
You're a capitalist.

00:37:43.770 --> 00:37:45.270 align:middle line:84%
And Reagan scratched
his head a bit.

00:37:45.270 --> 00:37:48.540 align:middle line:84%
And Reagan said, you
know, the only way

00:37:48.540 --> 00:37:52.910 align:middle line:84%
he could possibly envision
us working together

00:37:52.910 --> 00:37:54.500 align:middle line:84%
is if we were invaded
by the Martians.

00:37:54.500 --> 00:37:56.812 align:middle line:90%


00:37:56.812 --> 00:37:58.770 align:middle line:84%
And then Gorbachev
scratched his head and said,

00:37:58.770 --> 00:38:01.590 align:middle line:84%
well, you may have
a point there.

00:38:01.590 --> 00:38:04.350 align:middle line:84%
You see, if there's another
tribe out there that's hostile,

00:38:04.350 --> 00:38:08.370 align:middle line:84%
the Martians, then us human
tribes have to get together.

00:38:08.370 --> 00:38:10.570 align:middle line:84%
And perhaps we can
put aside the Cold War

00:38:10.570 --> 00:38:14.354 align:middle line:84%
and all the animosities
of the '50s and the '40s.

00:38:14.354 --> 00:38:16.020 align:middle line:84%
Well, the question
that we ask ourselves

00:38:16.020 --> 00:38:20.560 align:middle line:84%
today is, if we are
our own worst enemies,

00:38:20.560 --> 00:38:23.580 align:middle line:84%
if our technology, the crowning
achievements of the human mind,

00:38:23.580 --> 00:38:25.930 align:middle line:84%
is what could also
doom us, then will

00:38:25.930 --> 00:38:27.750 align:middle line:90%
we have planetary consciousness?

00:38:27.750 --> 00:38:31.990 align:middle line:84%
Will we begin to think of
the human race as a tribe?

00:38:31.990 --> 00:38:33.440 align:middle line:90%
That's not clear to me.

00:38:33.440 --> 00:38:33.940 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:38:33.940 --> 00:38:37.520 align:middle line:84%
And if you don't believe
me, go to the Balkans.

00:38:37.520 --> 00:38:41.120 align:middle line:84%
Go to places on the Earth
where ethnic cleansing

00:38:41.120 --> 00:38:43.800 align:middle line:90%
is the name of the game.

00:38:43.800 --> 00:38:45.790 align:middle line:84%
And if we think, we're
above ethnic cleansing,

00:38:45.790 --> 00:38:48.890 align:middle line:84%
what did we do with
the Native Americans?

00:38:48.890 --> 00:38:51.460 align:middle line:84%
The Native Americans
were put on reservations.

00:38:51.460 --> 00:38:53.873 align:middle line:84%
That's commonly called
ethnic cleansing.

00:38:53.873 --> 00:38:54.840 align:middle line:90%
OK?

00:38:54.840 --> 00:38:59.070 align:middle line:84%
So the question is, can we
enlarge our sense of tribe?

00:38:59.070 --> 00:39:00.560 align:middle line:90%
I don't know, OK.

00:39:00.560 --> 00:39:03.761 align:middle line:84%
It was mentioned here the
experiences of World War II.

00:39:03.761 --> 00:39:05.260 align:middle line:84%
During World War
II, my parents were

00:39:05.260 --> 00:39:08.750 align:middle line:84%
put in a concentration
camp in California.

00:39:08.750 --> 00:39:09.590 align:middle line:90%
OK?

00:39:09.590 --> 00:39:15.490 align:middle line:84%
We were not members of the tribe
of Californians back in 1942,

00:39:15.490 --> 00:39:17.591 align:middle line:90%
after Pearl Harbor.

00:39:17.591 --> 00:39:18.090 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:39:18.090 --> 00:39:21.690 align:middle line:84%
So the question is, are we
going to attain type one status

00:39:21.690 --> 00:39:23.200 align:middle line:84%
at a conscious
level, even though we

00:39:23.200 --> 00:39:26.920 align:middle line:84%
may have the instruments of
a planetary civilization,

00:39:26.920 --> 00:39:29.600 align:middle line:84%
a planetary internet,
a planetary television

00:39:29.600 --> 00:39:33.190 align:middle line:84%
system, a planetary
way of exchanging

00:39:33.190 --> 00:39:34.440 align:middle line:90%
personal experiences?

00:39:34.440 --> 00:39:35.826 align:middle line:90%
It's not clear to me.

00:39:35.826 --> 00:39:36.700 align:middle line:90%
It's not clear to me.

00:39:36.700 --> 00:39:39.940 align:middle line:84%
However, I will, with
every fiber of my body,

00:39:39.940 --> 00:39:43.250 align:middle line:84%
try to build a
world where we will

00:39:43.250 --> 00:39:45.630 align:middle line:84%
have that planetary
consciousness, where

00:39:45.630 --> 00:39:50.310 align:middle line:84%
the smallest unit of our
existence is the entire earth.

00:39:50.310 --> 00:39:54.101 align:middle line:84%
I will work with every fiber
of my body to see that happen.

00:39:54.101 --> 00:39:56.350 align:middle line:84%
Because I saw what happened
to my parents' generation.

00:39:56.350 --> 00:40:00.280 align:middle line:84%
And I don't want that to happen
in my children's generation.

