their paradigm.

00:42:46.770 --> 00:42:49.030 align:middle line:84%
And all I'm trying
to say, Michio,

00:42:49.030 --> 00:42:52.890 align:middle line:84%
is there's a lot of evidence,
very interesting evidence

00:42:52.890 --> 00:42:56.210 align:middle line:84%
out there that,
both biologically

00:42:56.210 --> 00:42:59.020 align:middle line:84%
